snippet: An Islamist charity plans to send a new aid flotilla to the Gaza Strip this year to challenge Israel’s naval blockade there, the group announced Tuesday.
abstract: Islamist charity Turkish Foundation for Human Rights and Freedoms and Humanitarian Relieve plans to send aid flotilla to Gaza Strip to challenge Israel's navel blockade.
lead_paragraph: An Islamist charity plans to send a new aid flotilla to the Gaza Strip this year to challenge Israel’s naval blockade there, the group announced Tuesday.
